title: MisterMusic Show 310 -new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 310 [120 minutes] 193kbps MP3 Stereo-




New music on this show from alternative rock's A Sunny Day In Glasgow, and psych/electronic band Bear In Heaven. 
The 'Oldie of the Week' is a big hit from 31 years ago. It stayed number 1 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart for the entire month of July, and later was named the biggest hit of 1983.

Plus a mix of over 5 decades of rock, indie and alternative music.


The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
